import re

def evaluate_word_sets_order_and_frequency(phrase1: str, phrase2: str) -> bool:
    p1 = re.sub('[^\\w]', ' ', phrase1).lower().split()
    p2 = re.sub('[^\\w]', ' ', phrase2).lower().split()
    return p1 != p2
